data.description: Escape the hustle and bustle of town and embrace the peace and quiet of a rural paradise in this home! With a sprawling yard that dreams are made of, this home is a perfect for nature enthusiasts and those seeking a great place for a private garden. The possibilities for outdoor entertaining or simply unwinding in your own slice of heaven are truly endless!The home has three bedrooms, two baths and a large living area complete with built-in cabinetry.But that's not all! This property is also conveniently located close to Post, allowing you to enjoy the best of both worlds - a peaceful rural lifestyle, yet within easy reach of Post, shopping, schools, and more.Call now to schedule your private tour and let your dreams become a reality.
